snow-raker
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number: 1
Definition:a person involved in tracking down and tramping out sheep buried in snow.
Origin:[none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain:Rural
Region:[none]
